ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 232, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 232 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA, with respect to the spring flooding that occurred from April 22, 2020 to May 4, 2020.
